ScriptExecutionDTO Data Type

The results of running a script under the context of an action. Contains messages that resulted from its execution

Properties
name data type description
objects_patch ScriptExecutionPatchDTO The patch to apply to the input objects of the script
tasks_added array of ScriptExecutionPatchDTO The tasks to add to the incident
notes_added array of ScriptExecutionPatchDTO The notes to add to the incident
task_notes_added array of ScriptExecutionPatchDTO The notes to add to the task
note_replies array of ScriptExecutionPatchDTO The replies to add to the note
milestones_added array of ScriptExecutionPatchDTO The milestones to add to the incident
artifacts_added array of ScriptExecutionPatchDTO The artifacts to add to the incident
rows_added object The rows to add to the given data tables
messages array of ScriptExecutionMessageDTO The messages returned from running the script
